title: South Africa 2 Year Note Yield
description: South Africa 2 Year Bond Yield was 7.22 percent on Monday November 7, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the South Africa 2 Year Note Yield reached an all time high of 22.55 in September of 1998. This page includes a chart with historical data for South Africa 2Y.
